{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"72b96cc1fe","title":"四方面军应迅速北上","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"8e09052c1f","index":0,"year":1935,"month":7,"day":10,"articleId":"72b96cc1fe"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji7-2","name":"毛泽东全集第7卷(2)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji7-2.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji7-2":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"1a23e3ed32","type":"paragraph","text":"四方面军应迅速北上","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"72b96cc1fe"},{"id":"54cafa790b","type":"paragraph","text":"（1935年7月10日）张：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"72b96cc1fe"},{"id":"7991e3886a","type":"paragraph","text":"甲、分路迅速北上原则早经确定，后忽延识，致无后续部队跟进。切盼如来电所指，各部真能速调速进，勿再延退，坐令敌占先机。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"72b96cc1fe"},{"id":"f9f4fac4e7","type":"paragraph","text":"乙、目前四方面军主力未到黑河坝东北，沿途番民P乱。三军团须使用于配置警戒及打通石确楼方面。一军团及八十八、八十九两师三团在毛儿盖未攻下前，不便突入。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"72b96cc1fe"},{"id":"524a5c3619","type":"paragraph","text":"丙、弟等今抵上芦花，急盼兄及徐陈速来集中指挥","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"72b96cc1fe"},{"id":"411e12b84c","type":"paragraph","text":"朱毛周","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"72b96cc1fe"},{"id":"7e77c66cc0","type":"paragraph","text":"十号","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"72b96cc1fe"},{"id":"6cc0e43249","type":"paragraph","text":"[111935年6月28日中共中央政治局根据两河口会议精神，作出《关于一、四方面军会合后的战略方针的决定》，提出集中主力向北进攻，在运动战中大量消灭敌人，首先取得甘肃南部，以创造川陕甘苏区根据地。红军第四方面军主要领导人张国森会上同意中央北上方针，会后延迟执行。这是毛泽东和朱德、周恩来给张国森的电报。","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"72b96cc1fe"},{"id":"2f0b899611","type":"paragraph","text":"[2]指当时四川西部的少数民族。那时他们因对红军不了解，一时有用对待国民党军队的办法来对待红军的现象。","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"72b96cc1fe"},{"id":"619cfaf6b6","type":"paragraph","text":"[3]徐陈，指徐向前、陈昌浩，当时分别任红军第四方面军总指挥和总","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"72b96cc1fe"}],"page":{"id":"c1af984e6a","publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"72b96cc1fe","start":188,"end":188}}}},"__N_SSG":true}